rComments: Man could be an auctioneer, he talks so fast. He reads off his slides but doesn't post them. Flies through slides, and unless you type at 300 words per minute you're not getting everything. Save yourself the grief and spend your time doing and understanding the reading instead of going to class.

Talks way too fast and doesnt post lecture slides. Video record or voice record if possible. He only reads off his slides rarely says anything outside the slides. His tests are basically all from lecture but supplemented by reading. Focus on necessary and sufficient causes for theories
There was class participation in a class of over 200. Very hard grader. Lectures were disorganized and confusing. Would avoid taking.
